<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Hossana Ti Zelin A w</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hossana ti zelin aw Halleluijah Amen;
 Lal Krista a hung pieng ie Bethlehem a chun,
 A paukam suok hehpih thu namtin damna ahi.
 Lawpin kiko hitiu, &quot;Hossana&quot; tiin

[V2]
 Aw Bethlehem tang chungah,
 Kumsawt kawlni no a suok aw, gen viel hitiu;
 Kuole zie hinna vakchu pakbang lawpa pawm ta'n
 Albang dah, luonthi nulna thuok talo ding.

[V3]
 2. A makin a lopi ie, kichamna Lengmang chu,
 Hehpih damtui a luon sak sietlei gam ahin;
 Gitoh apata I pawtdawk theihna ding ahi,
 Hehpih gam Lal ahi I Lalpau Isu.

[V4]
 3. Pa hun tiem a hungtung tai ei di'n damna ahi,
 Hehpihna a luong let hi Kalvari a chun,
 Amak zie kuoa gen thei sietlei mihiem aw hin,
 Hehpihna gamah naubang ei pui ina.

[V5]
 4. Zion lopina Lalmang, albang mang ei hawlpa,
 Van khawpite'n it mahleu a nang zo puou ie;
 Bangkima bangkim chunga Lalpen hen la Amen'
 Ei hehpihna kuoman a nielthei puou ie.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>10</hymn_number>
<author>Suakliana</author>
</song>